Titolo: The Legend of Blacksilver

Anno: 1988

Descrizione: The Legend of Blacksilver is a fantasy role-playing video game developed by Charles W. Dougherty and John C. Dougherty  of Quest, Inc. and published by Epyx in 1988.  It is an indirect sequel to the game Legacy of the Ancients. Originally designed for the Commodore 64, the game was ported to the Apple II.